				- Credits: <a href="http://theinspirationgallery.com"
					title="The Inspiration Gallery">Inspiration Gallery</a>
			</div>
			<div id="l">
				<a href="http://validator.w3.org/check?uri=referer" title="Validate">XHTML</a>
